'''Aseggas n Ilu''', neɣ '''Ɛam Ulfil''' ({{Lang-ar|عام الفيل}}عام الفيل), d issem i d-yefka umezruy [[Islam|ineslem]] i useggas iqerben ɣer 570 seld talalit n [[Ɛisa]]. Amezruy Ineslem yeqqar belli deg useggas-a nnbi n [[Islam|Tineslemt]] [[Muḥemmed]] ([[taɛrabt]]: مُـحَـمَّـد‎) ilul.<ref name="Hajjah">Hajjah Adil, Amina, "''Prophet Muhammad''", ISCA, Jun 1, 2002, {{ISBN|1-930409-11-7}}</ref> Issem agi yekka-d seg ayen yeḍran di [[Mekka]]. [[Abraha]] n [[Ḥabaca]], amenbaḍ [[Tamasiḥit|Amasiḥi]] n [[Yaman]], igḍefren [[Tagelda n Aksum]] di [[Ityupya]],<ref name="DACB">[http://www.dacb.org/stories/ethiopia/_abraha.html "Abraha."] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160113213718/http://www.dacb.org/stories/ethiopia/_abraha.html|date=2016-01-13}} ''Dictionary of African Christian Biographies''. 2007. (last accessed 11 April 2007)</ref><ref name="Muller">[http://www.yemenweb.com/info/_disc/0000002c.htm Walter W. Müller, "Outline of the History of Ancient Southern Arabia," in Werner Daum (ed.), ''Yemen: 3000 Years of Art and Civilisation in Arabia Felix''. 1987.] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141010075912/http://www.yemenweb.com/info/_disc/0000002c.htm|date=2014-10-10}}</ref> yelḥa ɣer [[Kaɛba]] di [[Mekka]] s yigen ameqqran, deg igen agi llan yiwen neɣ aṭaṣ n [[ilaten n umgaru]], iswi-is ad-tiseɣli ([[Kaɛba]]). Akken yeqqar wensay ineslem, ilu amezwaru, yettwasnen s yissem n Meḥmud ([[Taɛrabt]]: مَـحْـمُـوْد)<ref>{{Lien web|url=http://islaam.net/main/display.php?id=1480&category=176|title=Tafsir of Surah al Fil - The Elephant (Surah 105)|author=ʿAbdu r-Rahmān ibn Nāsir as-Saʿdī|work=Translated by Abū Rumaysah|publisher=Islamic Network|accessdate=15 March 2013}} </ref>, ibedd ɣer unekcum n [[Mekka]], d yugi adyekcem. Isenmezruyen fkan tiẓri yeqqaren belli aṭṭan yeṭfen ilu nni d ur yeǧǧa-t adyekcem ɣer [[Mekka]].<ref>{{cite journal|author=[[John S. Marr|Marr JS]], Hubbard E, Cathey, JT|date=2015|title=The Year of the Elephant|url=https://en.wikiversity.org/wiki/The_Year_of_the_Elephant|journal=Wikiversity Journal of Medicine|publisher=|volume=2|issue=1|pages=|doi=10.15347/wjm/2015.003|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150526193449/https://en.wikiversity.org/wiki/The_Year_of_the_Elephant|archivedate=2015-05-26|df=}}CS1 maint: Multiple names: authors list ([//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Category:CS1_maint:_Multiple_names:_authors_list link]) {{cite journal|author=[[John S. Marr|Marr JS]], Hubbard E, Cathey, JT|date=2015|title=The Year of the Elephant|url=https://en.wikiversity.org/wiki/The_Year_of_the_Elephant|journal=Wikiversity Journal of Medicine|publisher=|volume=2|issue=1|pages=|doi=10.15347/wjm/2015.003|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150526193449/https://en.wikiversity.org/wiki/The_Year_of_the_Elephant|archivedate=2015-05-26|df=}}<br />In turn citing: {{Adlis|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=TXEFAAAAQAAJ&pgis=1}}</ref>Iferrayen imaynuten deg Unẓul n [[Tazunegzirt Taɛrabt|Tuzunegzirt Taɛrabt]] ttciciden belli Aseggas n Ilu yeḍra-d di 569 neɣ 568, imi [[Tagelda n Isasaniyen|Tgelda n Isasaniyen]] tseɣli inabaḍen di [[Yaman]] igḍefren [[Tagelda n Aksum|Tgelda n Aksum]] di tama n 570. Maca, isenmezruyen ass-a ttamnen belli tagunit agi teḍra-d mraw n iseggasen send talalit n nnbi n [[Tineslemt|Tneslemt]].<ref name="The Oxford Dictionary of Islam">Esposito (2003). ''The Oxford Dictionary of Islam'', {{ISBN|0-19-512558-4}}, Oxford University Press</ref>

